snippet.title: Big Sky Infinity Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Big Sky Infinity: A fast paced, twin-stick shooter, guaranteed to keep you on your toes, you'll never play the same game twice!

The game will be available free of charge for a limited time to PlayStation Plus members in the European region.

http://bigskyinfinity.com
